SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",$__interval),
  avg(lat) AS "lat"
FROM geo
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time") AND
  "time" <= '$turnaround'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",$__interval),
  avg(lat) AS "lat"
FROM geo
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time") AND
  "time" >= '$turnaround'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1
